    "longBusinessSummary": "Tien Son Thanh Hoa Group Joint Stock Company engages in the agricultural products trading, factory leasing, and garment manufacturing businesses in the United States, South Korea, and internationally. The company is involved in garment sewing; wholesale of other construction materials and installation equipment; wholesale business; mining of stone, sand, gravel, clay; construction of all kinds of houses; short-term accommodation services; loading and unloading of goods; trading in real estate, land use rights owned, used or leased; selling spare parts and auxiliary parts of automobiles and other motor vehicles. It also engages in the wholesale of raw agricultural and forestry products and live animals; wholesale of other machinery, equipment and spare parts; construction of railways and roads; restaurants and mobile catering services; road freight transport; vocational education; activities of centers, agencies for consulting, introducing and brokering labor and employment; brokerage and auction agents, and processing of agricultural and forestry products, import and export of construction materials, agricultural products, lacquerware products and textiles. The company was founded in 1995 and is based in Thanh Hoá, Vietnam.",
